snippet: Recently discovered pages are from an earlier version of “To Kill a Mockingbird,” a rare books expert has concluded.
abstract: Rare books expert James S Jaffe says recently discovered manuscript pages by Harper Lee are from early version of To Kill a Mockingbird, and do not represent possible third novel by author.
lead_paragraph: Recently discovered pages are from an earlier version of “To Kill a Mockingbird,” a rare books expert has concluded.

headline.main: Expert Says Manuscript Is Not Harper Lee’s Third Novel
headline.print_headline: Expert Says Manuscript Is Not Lee’s Third Novel
